SKULLrs. The old school little game for 1 human player.

/ / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / /

The SKULLrs are shooting devastating high energy pulses to the ground.

How many times can you intercept these pulses?

Use only your [space] key while playing.
